snippet.textDisplay:
Hi Siddharth

I am a die hard ARR fan. But I don't understand why people on youtube are discussing about dislikes on his videos.
We must understand that this is just 'dislike' button and NOT HATE.
Even an ARR fan can dislike some of his compositions (although I never :P)
And as far as we (ARR fans) know him even he himself appreciates some critical response for his compositions :-)

snippet.textDisplay: Beautiful composition! Rahman sir sings it so confidently like Bangla is imbibed into him! The initial piece on the Harpejji reminded me of Rehna Tu's alaap. Mohini Dey on the Bass and Keba on the Acoustic Guitar were awesome as usual.. Sivamani sir's Konnakkol was too precise and I wish Prasanna sir had got a little more spotlight. Looking forward to his other compositions of the season..till then, on a loop! :)
snippet.textOriginal: Beautiful composition! Rahman sir sings it so confidently like Bangla is imbibed into him! The initial piece on the Harpejji reminded me of Rehna Tu's alaap. Mohini Dey on the Bass and Keba on the Acoustic Guitar were awesome as usual.. Sivamani sir's Konnakkol was too precise and I wish Prasanna sir had got a little more spotlight.
